      "content": "subjective value is just a distraction though. it's a cope. if we're being strictly logical, if there is no objective truth or cosmic scale, then a person's existence is just a variable. if that variable equals zero or one, the outcome for the universe is identical. so if you strip away the \"feelings,\" isn't it more logical to accept that there's no reason to prefer living over not living? it's just a mathematical wash.",
